description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 62, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 186, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Box for East, 3 for South, and Stringalong for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90623-34372-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [186 Votes, Top 5% Score]
